"title": "5302: education",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5302: education",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The imparting of spiritual, intellectual, moral and social instruction, the basis for which is the fear of the LORD. People continue learning throughout the whole of life. The education of children in the OT was centred on the home and synagogue and was largely of a religious and ethical nature. In the NT, children were included in the community of the church, but the home was still the main sphere of their education.</p>\n<h2>The fear of the LORD is the basis for all education</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:10\">PSA 111:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:5\">2CH 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:12\">PSA 25:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">PRO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:1-Prov2:8\">PRO 2:1–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">PRO 15:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:3\">ISA 11:1–11:3</a></p>\n<h2>Faith is an essential element of Christian education</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:3\">HEB 11:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Education should not oppose the truth about God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:5\">2CO 10:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:6\">MAT 18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:20-1Tim6:21\">1TI 6:20–6:21</a></p>\n<h2>Education should emphasise that the world has a richness and coherence derived from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:1\">PSA 24:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3\">JHN 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:7-Job12:10\">JOB 12:7–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:5-Ps104:26\">PSA 104:5–104:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:26\">1CO 10:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:17\">COL 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Education in the home</h2>\n<h3>Through parental instruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4-Deut6:9\">DEU 6:4–6:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:4-Ps78:6\">PSA 78:4–78:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:9-Deut4:10\">DEU 4:9–4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:20-Deut6:25\">DEU 6:20–6:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:18-Deut11:21\">DEU 11:18–11:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:6\">PRO 22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:19\">ISA 38:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:4\">EPH 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:21\">COL 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of parents teaching their children</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:19\">GEN 18:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:1-Prov31:9\">PRO 31:1–31:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14-2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:14–3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Through parental example</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:5\">2TI 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:31-2Chr20:32\">2CH 20:31–20:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:3-2Chr26:4\">2CH 26:3–26:4</a></p>\n<h3>Through discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:15\">PRO 29:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">PRO 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:13\">TIT 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>Education through religious worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:34-Josh8:35\">JOS 8:34–8:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:13\">2CH 20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:21\">EZR 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:43\">NEH 12:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:15-Matt21:16\">MAT 21:15–21:16</a></p>\n<h2>Education through religious festivals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:9-Deut31:13\">DEU 31:9–31:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:24-Exod12:27\">EXO 12:24–12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:6-Exod13:8\">EXO 13:6–13:8</a></p>",
